# Real Data Only (AR-local)

## Philosophy

Validation should reflect **real CDR shapes** and **real generated artifacts**. Fabricated rows or fake exports can pass while real ingest fails.

## Rule

- **Do not** invent rate rows, provider lists, or JSON/XLSX content as substitutes for running ingest or using existing **`runs/<date>/_exports/`** output.
- **Do** use exports produced by **`cdr_daily.py`** / **`cdr_outputs.py`** (or fixtures captured from real runs if you add tests later).
- **Pure helpers** (string slugify, path parsing) may use tiny literal inputs.
- **Dashboard work:** point **`--exports`** at a real **`dashboard-cache`** tree so **`/api/latest`** and charts reflect actual data.

See **`AGENTS.md`** (Project philosophy: real data only).
